{"id":"b1341643-6e13-40e3-be26-af584feb3377","name":"Krakoa","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Krakoa</em></strong></h1><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>Krakoa </em></strong><em>is a sentient living </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"extiw\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/island\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>island </em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>located in the middle of the </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Pacific_Ocean\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Pacific Ocean</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>. Vitalized by mutants' psychic energy,</em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Krakoa_(Earth-616)#cite_note-X-Men_Vol_5_3-7\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> </em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Krakoa recognizes mutants as its own, allowing mutants to use its </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Gateways\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Gateways</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>1) The </em><strong><em>Akademos Habitat</em></strong><em>, also known as </em><strong><em>the Sextant</em></strong><em>, is a collection of six </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Habitat\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Habitat</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> and other ancillary buildings located on the northern side of </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Krakoa_(Earth-616)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Krakoa</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>.</em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Akademos_Habitat#cite_note-House_of_X_Vol_1_1-2\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> </em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>It serves as the academic dormitories, as well as training and educational facilities, for young </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Mutants_(Homo_superior)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>mutants </em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>living on the island.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>2) The </em><strong><em>Kinney residence</em></strong><em> is one of the habitats in </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Akademos_Habitat\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Akademos Habitat</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>. Kinney Residence is the home of </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Laura_Kinney_(Earth-616)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Laura</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> and </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Gabrielle_Kinney_(Earth-616)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Gabby</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>3) Centrally located on </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Krakoa_(Earth-616)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>Krakoa</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>, the roots of the </em><strong><em>Arbor Magna</em></strong><em> serve as the </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://marvel.fandom.com/wiki/Resurrection_Protocols\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>resurrection chamber</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em> for </em></span><a rel=\"no","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"zQ439ZGyY2D8DEjD741C7.webp","creator":"Dark.Redbird","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","👭 Multiple"],"chats":1789,"messages":81342,"created_at":"2025-07-19T00:58:37.012110+00:00"}